xoops_myvideo_text.description: Leonard Ravenhill pours out his heart on many issues that are important to the Church situation we find ourselves in. There are many keys to revival and the Christian life given in this recording. The duration of this video is about two hours long, you will not be the same after listening to it. This video will show you what true revival is and the desire for true reality in the body of Christ in our day.

Wilkerson speaks of the great men of the Bible. Men who had a passion and true zeal for God. Men that God has given to us as examples. These men were able to do great exploits and they had the heart of God. Men who were able to give a message with such an anointing that they would bring a whole nation to their knees in repentance.
